| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6908 — Recovery Inhibition (tengu)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cc186517-3f1c-5539-8bd2-892af37a9b15"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
